data.Name: Feed Me
data.Bio: There is more than one artist called Feed Me. 1) Feed Me is Jon Gooch (AKA Spor)'s complextro/brostep project. The first release by Feed Me was 'Mordez Moi', on Noisia's Division label, the second was 'The Spell / Raw Chicken' released on Mau5trap. After completing a stack of remixes for the likes of Gorillaz, Chase & Status and Chris Lake, Feed Me released his much anticipated 'Feed Me's Big Adventure EP' (also on Mau5trap) exclusively to Beatport on Christmas Day 2010.
